---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title='Workflow Automation'
  description='Transform your business operations with durable, scalable workflow automation using modern orchestration platforms like Temporal.'
>
  <div class="high-contrast-section bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-700">
    <h2 class="text-slate-100">Short Description</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-200 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      I specialize in building reliable, scalable workflow automation solutions using modern orchestration platforms like Temporal. By implementing durable execution patterns and robust error handling, I help businesses automate complex processes while ensuring reliability and maintainability.
    </p>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>

<style>
  .example-project {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .example-project h3 {
    color: theme(colors.blue.300);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .results {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }
</style>
